  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A new $4,000 depot is being\nplanned for the o. r. & N. and, it\nis reported, work will begin on it\nin the near future. The depot will\nbe situated on the south side of\nthe o. r. G. N. tracks between\nHoward and Washington streets.\nThis fine new building will take\nthe place of the old shed which has\nbeen used in past years."
    }
